{"type":"message","id":"fb781e08","parentId":"b4a96b34","timestamp":"2026-04-05T14:26:24.563Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 你好。  \n我在，刚刚收到你的测试消息了。\n\n这是个全新工作区，还没完成“我是谁 / 你是谁”的初始化。要不我们顺手把它定一下：\n\n- 你希望我怎么称呼你？\n- 你想让我叫什么名字？\n- 我走什么风格：冷静、直接、温和、毒舌一点、还是别的？\n\n如果你懒得想，我也可以先临时用一个默认设定开始。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0ea17a1053dd6ec10169d270fe23dc819b9d29c362ef32a248\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":22416,"output":114,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":22530,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775399156195,"responseId":"resp_0ea17a1053dd6ec10169d270fd5754819b986d5a6018fa412f"}}
